  "chunk_type": "subsection",
  "content": "Prerequisite: Str 40, Strength domain.\nBenefit: If required to make an opposed roll involving Strength (including grapple checks), the deity receives a divine bonus of +25 on its roll. This bonus stacks with the normal divine rank bonus.\nSuggested Portfolio Elements: Strength.",
